16239,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T14:01:49.000Z","msg":"我自己都係仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知點解啲老母真係好撚偏心大哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我學費要自己交<br />\n但大哥學費老母全包<br />\n仲要已經諗好咗送俾層樓我大哥<br />\n大哥仲要廢青嚟<br />\n但我毛都冇條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有好多不能盡錄"},{"pid":"77e55b5e96d40b2360c79f6afddb18e8616ca78e","tid":2156371,"uid":16239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57f1878bb7a2467bd1b56611f719be8ae1ce0d15","tid":2156371,"uid":89861,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"fad6a59bc62291cf8e4c9ed8533e4cb65f42c323","tid":2156371,"uid":213945,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T12:56:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T12:59:56.000Z","msg":"你係女？定個樣生得冇哥靚？<br />\n事實上一出世己經睇樣、包括你父母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T14:04:08.000Z","msg":"難講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然我唔係靚仔<br />\n但靚仔過我大哥（唔係我話，係聽過啲uncle auntie咁同我老母講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n但一樣偏心阿哥<br />\n或者可能佢心目中阿哥最靚仔啦"},{"pid":"3737adae6196986f9affa667a18ff764ce1180b5","tid":2156371,"uid":257593,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"f9e3b1fdf2c052bd8657c3c8a3b9994558fd6f2a","tid":2156371,"uid":274123,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T13:30:47.000Z","msg":"呀哥從來冇做過家務<br />\n廁所廁紙用完都唔會幫手換個種<br />\n但如果我食完野唔洗碗<br />\n又或者只洗自己個份唔幫呀哥洗<br />\n就會被老母吊<br />\n老母名言：咁你係女仔呀嘛，應該做<br />\n真係好唔gur"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T14:05:26.000Z","msg":"我煮完攞埋俾呀媽食 呀媽講唔該 都即刻gur哂 <br />\n點知老豆好撚賤格咁話：使乜唔該啫，呢啲嘢佢應份架 <br />\n激死我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時對細佬講嘢大聲啲都唔捨得<br />\n對住我就當我工人"},{"pid":"3e36a601cc1fe90f5a79c8bd461c1688481444f7","tid":2156371,"uid":100596,"like":0,"